  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13099187/eurostar-snow-7-838x330-hero.jpg" alt="heroview" data-udi="umb://media/a108b997dac543acb7afc0de16fe7cd6" /></p>
<h2>Travel by train this winter on the Eurostar</h2>
<p>Eurostar is back for the second year running with its fantastic ski train. The <strong>Eurostar Snow train </strong>for the 2024/25 ski season can be booked as part of Inghams package holiday and we here at Inghams are on-board for this journey, because it’s…</p>
<h2>Rewarding</h2>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13099192/eurostar-snow-4-838x300.jpg" alt="rewardinghero" data-udi="umb://media/44251ee7f7464c57aea4e39bef12a89b" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>Enjoy the spectacular views as you travel across Europe to the stunning town of Bourg-Saint-Maurice. With comfy seats and generous legroom, you can sit back and relax or even sleep while the countryside passes you by.</p>
<p>Train travel is ideal with a family. With the Eurostar Snow train, there is always plenty of room, so toys and games to entertain your children is not an issue space wise. Plus, if you don’t want to pack a picnic, the trains on-board Cafe provides a variety of food and drink.</p>
<p>The biggest reward travelling via Eurostar Snow is that you get extra time on the slopes. The train departs home again from Bourg-Saint-Maurice on Sundays at 8:09am, returning to London St Pancras International at 15.57pm. This means you have an extra full day of skiing on Saturdays.</p>
<h2>Relaxing </h2>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13099200/eurostar-12-500x500.jpg" alt="reasonablehero1" data-udi="umb://media/1f16e02a1a1d4220a6567e9d7466f3c2" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13099202/eurostar-snow-11-500x500.jpg" alt="reasonablehero2" data-udi="umb://media/8bf6f5a63db448a7998a262aee814ee0" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>Once on-board, you can just enjoy the journey and service provided by the Eurostar Snow train. On an Inghams ski holiday, your transfers are covered from when you arrive in Bourg-St-Maurice to your chosen resort, as well as your hotel (the lovely Base Camp Lodge) being included for the Saturday evening before your return home.</p>
<p>The great thing about train travel is there is no weight limit on bags as with airlines or no limited space as with your car, so you can pack what you like and not just what you need. So, make the most of this and add those extra thermal layers or spare pair of goggles to your suitcase. With Eurostar Snow offering generous luggage allowance, each traveller can have two suitcases, one piece of hand luggage and skis or snowboard at no extra cost.</p>
<p>Eurostar Snow makes a quiet stop at Lille. Here, it leaves you plenty of time to get off, help your children, and gather your bags and walk across the platform to your waiting connection. <img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13093140/smallreindeer200x288.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2b5a38469dd244b7bf93deb57bf6bd97" /></p>
<h2>Reachable </h2>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13099191/eurostar-snow-2-838x300.jpg" alt="reachablehero" data-udi="umb://media/4851788317e3472490ce23c8cef9451d" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>Eurostar Snow train will be running from the 21st of December to the 22nd of February, the ideal months for keen skiers who like to make the most of good snowfall.</p>
<p>As the train is travelling from London to Bourg-Saint-Maurice, it is an ideal location to reach some of the best resorts across France. With Inghams ski holidays, you will board a coach to go on to some fantastic ski areas including: <a data-udi="umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03" href="/{localLink:umb://document/3f107aa9435442a892636b72e6e40b03}" title="Tignes-Val d’Isere Ski Area">Tignes &amp; Val d’Isère</a>, and <a data-udi="umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/37e8bc9846b74cf1a001f969874ce05b}" title="Paradiski Ski Area">Paradiski</a>.</p>
<p>These areas offer renowned resorts such as:</p>
<ul>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/16c56b283bca4ae2b2ada820a5d3a03d}" title="Val d'Isere">Val d’Isere</a> in Tignes &amp; Val d’Isere - great of <a data-udi="umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079" href="/{localLink:umb://document/89595b9898014c5fbd93f5619c64b079}" title="Apres Ski Holidays">Après Ski</a> with the infamous La Folie Douce.</li>
<li><a data-udi="umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1424e5dc124549bebe48ab72e02ec9cb}" title="Les Arcs">Les Arcs</a> in Paradiski - great for <a data-udi="umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875" href="/{localLink:umb://document/a543e1407c404a978d9b4539252fc875}" title="Family Ski Holidays">families</a> with lots of practice areas for younger children and plenty of blue runs for <a data-udi="umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d336d627fb34bec960e3b7bc041f7e1}" title="Ski Holidays for Beginners">beginners</a> to gain confidence.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Reasonable</h2>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13099193/eurostar-snow-6-838x300.jpg" alt="relaxinghero" data-udi="umb://media/757d05a8878648b6bff47483a20636cc" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<p>Inghams is offering a package including the Eurostar Snow train for your ski holiday. Of course, if travelling with a bit of luxury is your style, you can upgrade from standard to premium standard.</p>
<p>Sustainability has become a key factor in day to day life as well as our holiday choices. As we all are paying more attention to the planet, opting for train travel over air travel is a great way to reduce your carbon footprint. This is important to Inghams too, which is why we are working with Eurostar Snow on offering this train as part of our ski holiday packages to help ensure we are going greener so our mountains don’t.</p>
<p>Believe it or not, you still make good time when opting to travel via the Eurostar Snow train. Leaving London at a reasonable time of 9am on Saturdays and arriving in Bourg-Saint-Maurice by 6pm the same day.</p>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4>Book your ski holiday by train:</h4>
<p><img src="/media/13099197/eurostar-snow-3-500x500-cta.jpg" alt="booknow" data-udi="umb://media/af31bb29670e4d508294a80b53ff3006" /></p>
<p>You can currently book the Eurostar Snow train over the phone. However, other train travel can be booked via the website by selecting London St Pancras as your departure location. </p>
<p><a href="tel:01483791111" class="InfinityNumber c-btn">Call us to book today</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="g6">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h4>Other destinations in France:</h4>
<p><img src="/media/13099198/eurostar-snow-5-500x500-cta.jpg" alt="franceresorts" data-udi="umb://media/1e802dbf630e4e7382cf849dbeee905e" /></p>
<p>Explore all that France has to offer, with fantastic resorts and many to choose from with an Inghams ski holiday. </p>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bd152c97eb204c59a0ae4a5b65e2c1e5}" title="France" class="c-btn">Resorts in France</a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p><img style="width: 0px; height: 0px;" src="/media/13093140/smallreindeer200x288.jpg?width=0&amp;height=0" alt="" data-udi="umb://media/2b5a38469dd244b7bf93deb57bf6bd97" /></p>
<div class="col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-grey c-card--generic-shadow ">
